# Deploy

Read [AGENTS.md](../../AGENTS.md) and [docs/DEPLOYMENT.md](../../docs/DEPLOYMENT.md).

- Production branch: `master`.
- User manages branches, pushes, and PRs manually.
- Push to `master` runs CI (Brakeman, RuboCop, model RSpec) then Kamal deploy when green.
- Secrets: GitHub environment `production`; local `.kamal/secrets` (gitignored).
- Do not edit deploy config or run Kamal/CI commands unless explicitly requested.
- Never commit `.env`, `config/master.key`, `.kamal/secrets`, or credentials.

PR reviews: [.cursor/BUGBOT.md](../BUGBOT.md) (deploy section).
